lead_paragraph: Rocco Mediate holed out from a greenside bunker for birdie on the par-3 17th to wrap up a record-setting, wire-to-wire victory Sunday in the Senior PGA Championship.

headline.print_headline: Rocco Mediate Wins Senior PGA Championship
